page.title: 20ENTERTAINMENT 2
page.content: {DARTS:}We have a darts team. They play in the{"BELL INN"} { FETES:}We have four fetes: Church, Youth club, School and we always have one car boot sale.{ { SCHOOL SPORTS: }We have skipping, shuttle reley, bean bag throwing, obstacle race, long distance and tug of war. {EUCHRE:}This card game is played in the{"BELL INN". { ANGLING:}At the reservoir people who have licenses can go trout fishing. {WALKING:}There are a number of footpaths in our block enabling people to walk through the fields. { SILVER LINING:}We have a club called The Silver Lining for the old people.
